{"id":319792,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-5-18登楼抗议被刑拘的张淑梅提起行政诉/","date":"2013-10-26T07:18:08Z","modified":"2013-10-26T07:18:08Z","title":"维权网 | “5.18登楼抗议”被刑拘的张淑梅提起行政诉讼（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员宗世石报道）今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日，张淑梅等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>位访民爬上“人大”附近的白楼，抗议司法的不公和信访部门的推诿扯皮，事后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>位维权访民悉数被以“寻衅滋事”的罪名非法拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>天后，都被取保候审。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张淑梅是当天登楼抗议的访民之一，她是黑龙江省伊春市人，因为和当地银行的经济纠纷得不到黑龙江各级法院的公正裁决来北京上访多年，上访维权不但她的诉求没有得到丝毫的解决，反被当地政府多次非法拘留、停掉她赖以生存的工资等等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>对通过政府规定的上访渠道来解决问题已经彻底绝望的张淑梅和其他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>位访民不得不以爬楼的方式来抗争。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>他们选择的地点是人大常委会附近的白楼，张淑梅说，之所以如此，是为了让中国法律的制定者、拥有最高权力的人看看，中国有这样一个访民群体，他们多年鸣冤叫屈在自称为首善之区的北京，因为是访民，得不到正常的公民待遇，随时被非法搜查、被非法关押，对访民来说已经成了家常便饭。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张淑梅认为作为一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">55</span><span>岁的女人她没有能力去寻什么衅，北京警方对她刑拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>天纯粹是欲加之罪，她更不想把犯罪嫌疑人的称号背一年，因而提起行政诉讼，状告北京市公安局西城分局。请示依法撤销对她“因寻衅滋事刑事拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>天”的错误决定和依法撤销对她“取保候审”的错误决定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-pjaHwrNHwqM/UmspRNpLCQI/AAAAAAAAqIg/mK1HRPcER4M/s1600/IMG_5375.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-pjaHwrNHwqM/UmspRNpLCQI/AAAAAAAAqIg/mK1HRPcER4M/s320/IMG_5375.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-LR4sikBz8-w/UmspVF3prpI/AAAAAAAAqIw/GBCRubWIeBE/s1600/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+011.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-LR4sikBz8-w/UmspVF3prpI/AAAAAAAAqIw/GBCRubWIeBE/s320/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+011.jpg\" width=\"268\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-iLv82vYhNMA/UmspTeT2JYI/AAAAAAAAqIo/hz2HRTxdKRw/s1600/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+012.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-iLv82vYhNMA/UmspTeT2JYI/AAAAAAAAqIo/hz2HRTxdKRw/s320/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+012.jpg\" width=\"213\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-6n-dmkYE2Sc/UmspaBccPlI/AAAAAAAAqJA/VIZgAe5Oegs/s1600/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+013.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-6n-dmkYE2Sc/UmspaBccPlI/AAAAAAAAqJA/VIZgAe5Oegs/s320/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+013.jpg\" width=\"213\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-vjKyCa9-YhY/UmspZCN4sSI/AAAAAAAAqI4/StCaXNZg96c/s1600/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+014.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-vjKyCa9-YhY/UmspZCN4sSI/AAAAAAAAqI4/StCaXNZg96c/s320/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+014.jpg\" width=\"230\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}